							</a>
							<a href="https://github.com/HrSkully" target="_blank" class="social-link px-6 py-2 bg-white/5 text-white border border-white/20 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:brightness-125 hover:shadow-[0_4px_12px_rgba(0,176,240,0.3)] min-w-[100px] text-center">
								GitHub
							</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</section>
